Everyone's favorite fragrant jeans are here.  
This is the chane* spring and summer style, so it is naturally on the lighter side.  
But this is currently the best-fitting denim in all my brands. The material is particularly comfortable and soft.  
I always get asked about these pants whenever I take photos for private use.  
I don't want to lose the original feel by switching to thicker denim for autumn and winter.  
So I made two versions: one with the original thickness and one with added fleece.  
The fleece version isn't as soft, but the cut is just as good-looking.  
And I added a dark gray color. Good pants should come in more colors.  
WUUUS 2024 F/W
src: 大家喜欢的香香牛仔裤做出来了 这条是chane*春夏款所以本身偏薄 但这条是目前我所有品牌牛仔裤里最好穿的材质特别舒服特别软 私下每次穿拍了照都会有网友问这条 我不想为了秋冬去换成很厚的牛仔布就失去了原版的味道 所以就做了两个版本 一个原版厚度一个加绒版  加绒版就没那么软了哈但裤型都是一样好看的 还加了一个黑灰色好穿的裤子就喜欢做多点颜色
